    <sect3>
        <title>base</title>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    Version number 4.3.1.0 (was 4.3.0.0)
                </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
                <para>
                    The Unicode support has been improved; in
                    particular, decoding errors are now detected,
                    and an exception raised, immediately, rather than
                    when a buffer gets flushed.
                </para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
                <para>
                    Some bugs, including memory leaks and a deadlock,
                    in the new IO manager on non-Windows have
                    been fixed.
                </para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </sect3>

